    <item>
      <title>受美国贸易威胁 加拿大考虑增加向中国运输石油的方式</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-05/canada-s-24-billion-trans-mountain-pipeline-accelerates-push-to-look-beyond-us</link>
      <description><![CDATA[自五月加拿大跨山输油管道扩建工程完工以来，几乎每天都有一艘满载油砂原油的油轮通过该管道穿过温哥华的狮门大桥，运往太平洋周围的炼油厂。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-05/canada-s-24-billion-trans-mountain-pipeline-accelerates-push-to-look-beyond-us</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 05 Feb 2025 13:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普称他希望新核协议能让伊朗“繁荣”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-05/trump-says-he-wants-new-nuclear-deal-allowing-iran-to-prosper</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国总统唐纳德·特朗普周三表示，他愿意立即开始与伊朗达成新的核协议，使伊朗能够“和平发展和繁荣”，这似乎软化了他对伊朗伊斯兰共和国的立场。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-05/trump-says-he-wants-new-nuclear-deal-allowing-iran-to-prosper</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 05 Feb 2025 12:15:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英美资源集团首席执行官称马里矿业发展令人深感担忧</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-05/anglo-ceo-says-mali-mining-developments-cause-for-grave-concern</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英美资源集团首席执行官邓肯·万布拉德表示，马里政府对采掘业的改革可能会阻止企业在该国投资，该国拥有世界第二大金矿。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-05/anglo-ceo-says-mali-mining-developments-cause-for-grave-concern</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 05 Feb 2025 12:01:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>俄克拉荷马州加入反 DEI 投资者行列，亚马逊、Alphabet 成为目标</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-05/amazon-alphabet-s-dei-efforts-targeted-by-oklahoma-investor-proposal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[俄克拉荷马州有望成为第一个试图利用其作为投资者的影响力来终止美国企业 DEI 的共和党州，其股东代理提案中的目标是包括亚马逊公司 (Amazon.com Inc.) 和 Alphabet Inc. 在内的公司。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-05/amazon-alphabet-s-dei-efforts-targeted-by-oklahoma-investor-proposal</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 05 Feb 2025 12:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>“边境争夺战”：特朗普即将加征关税 制造商陷入混乱</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-05/trump-tariffs-push-us-manufacturers-to-rush-to-beat-mexico-canada-fees</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在紧张的 72 小时内，唐纳德·特朗普总统威胁对加拿大、墨西哥和中国征收新的关税，导致股市和货币暴跌，并给全球贸易带来冲击。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-05/trump-tariffs-push-us-manufacturers-to-rush-to-beat-mexico-canada-fees</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 05 Feb 2025 11:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>卡尼提议取消加拿大资本利得税上调</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-05/carney-to-propose-scrapping-canada-s-capital-gains-tax-increase</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，马克·卡尼计划宣布，如果赢得自由党领袖竞选并成为总理，他将不会执行提高加拿大资本利得税的提议。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-05/carney-to-propose-scrapping-canada-s-capital-gains-tax-increase</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 05 Feb 2025 11:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
